dct_title_s: Cheesequake State Park, New Jersey, 1962, brochure front
dct_description_sm: Outside cover of brochure issued by the New Jersey Department of Conservation and Economic Development about Cheesequake State Park. This side features a table of campsites available campsites, bathing areas, cabin and boat rentals and hunting grounds. Photographic illustration on front flap.
